  <brief_title>Predictors of Response to Combined Pegylated Interferon and Ribavirin in Chronic Hepatitis C Infected Egyptian Patients</brief_title>
  <official_title>Phase 4 Predictors of Response to Combined Pegylated Interferon and Ribavirin in Chronic Hepatitis C Genotype IV Infected Egyptian Patients</official_title>
